{"title":"马年（外一首）","authors":["陈所巨"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":1,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"马年（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈所巨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马年之马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以急切的蹄声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲打浑厚的大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国这是最吉利的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是许多人瞩望中的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红与洁白的奔驰啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剽悍与强壮的骏马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生风的四蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾起时露出钢青的掌铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大地上，在黝黑大陆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与苍青海域"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量被崇拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信仰也被崇拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾、奔驰与奔放的年头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是最初的剽悍的征兆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是力量热情与速度的默契"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是中国人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋起与奔腾的起点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许因为马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许因为铿锵的蹄声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许因为在中国大地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电一样奔驰的希冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是马年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是中国人和中国骏马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信心百倍大冲刺的年头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周是喝采"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周是云彩啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片雪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在睫毛上融化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶莹的视区在冬之旷野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新年挂历一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一匹长嘶的白马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一年，这一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽而净洁的扉页"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是一片期待与希望广袤啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十年代　这个灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与辉煌的早春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在冰点之下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有热情的火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在马蹄和马背上席卷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片洁白的空旷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片雪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是冰清玉洁的美人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是梨花槐花稻花的先躯啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扬起面颊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感知融化的情绪的滋润与召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期待中的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那奔马神气活现四蹄生风＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}